{{Quote|I should be really angry at you. But I [[Attack on Karen Page|watched you fight for me]]. [[Attack on the Hand|Twice]], actually. You know I dreamed about that? I played it over in my mind again and again, and I keep... How can I be this mad at someone who saved my life?|Karen Page to [[Matt Murdock]]|Resurrection (Daredevil)}}
